attributes.long-description:
Fight more of the greatest Star Wars® Battles any way you want. Fight on the front lines where every weapon and vehicle is yours. Now for the first time, Star Wars®: Battlefront II™ lets you Fight as a Jedi, Battle in Space, and Play 13 new Locations. Defeat enemy ships and destroy the heavy cruisers and capital ships to achieve victory, or land within enemy territory and blow up a Star Destroyer from the inside. 

A minimum 704 MB of disk space is required.
